ks for both college & high school\n\n📌 Dashboard Upgrades – Add notes, show grades, clean up the sidebar, and more\n\nJoin over 1,500,000 students making Canvas actually work for them.\nBuilt by students, for students.\n\nDisclaimer: BetterCanvas is an independent project and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Instructure or Canvas LMS.\n\nSource Code: https://github.com/UseBetterCanvas/bettercanvas\nFirefox version: https://addons.mozilla.org/addon/better-canvas/","weeklyDownloads":766,"type":"extension","creator":{"name":"ksucpea","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/16396066/"},"developers":[],"screenshots":[{"url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/full/292/292524.png?modified=1753317289","width":1280,"height":800,"thumbnailURL":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/thumbs/292/292524.jpg?modified=1753317289","thumbnailWidth":533,"thumbnailHeight":333},{"url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/full/292/292525.png?modified=1753317289","width":1280,"height":800,"thumbnailURL":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/thumbs/292/292525.jpg?modified=1753317289","thumbnailWidth":533,"thumbnailHeight":333},{"url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/full/292/292526.png?modified=1753317289","width":1280,"height":800,"thumbnailURL":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/thumbs/292/292526.jpg?modified=1753317289","thumbnailWidth":533,"thumbnailHeight":333},{"url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/full/281/281514.png?modified=1753317289","width":1280,"height":800,"thumbnailURL":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/thumbs/281/281514.jpg?modified=1753317289","thumbnailWidth":533,"thumbnailHeight":333,"caption":"The menu where you can turn on features or customize dark mode"},{"url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/full/275/275190.png?modified=1753317289","width":1280,"height":800,"thumbnailURL":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/thumbs/275/275